Use the standard library
This is how to sort_even of l:
   Remember that evens is []
   Remember that n is l's length
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      When remainder of item i in l and 2 is 0, then:
         Add evens to item i in l
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   Remember that evens is bubble_sort of evens
   Remember that j is 0
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      When remainder of item i in l and 2 is 0, then:
         Remember that item i in l is item j in evens
         Increase j
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is l
